---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Website Policy | Jamail Hardwoods Houston"
  description="Read Jamail Hardwoods website policy, including privacy, cookies, and contact information."
>
  <Header />

  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-8">Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-brand-ink/60 mb-8">Last Updated: March 18, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6 text-brand-ink/80">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">1. Privacy and Personal Data</h2>
        <p>
          We collect information you provide when you contact us, request samples, or submit project details.
          We use this information only to respond to your requests, provide services, and improve your website experience.
          We do not sell or rent your personal information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">2. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses essential cookies for core site functionality and may use analytics tools to understand
          how visitors use the site. You can manage cookie preferences using the consent banner and your browser settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">3. Website Content</h2>
        <p>
          Product images, descriptions, and availability may change over time. We make reasonable efforts to keep
          information accurate, but final product selections, pricing, and timelines are confirmed directly with our team.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We may use third-party providers for hosting, analytics, and communication tools. These providers process
          data according to their own terms and privacy practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">5. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For policy-related questions or requests about your data, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:info@jamailfloors.com" class="text-brand-brass underline"> info@jamailfloors.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mt-8 mb-4">6. Related Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          For full details on how we collect, use, and protect information, visit our
          <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-brand-brass underline"> Privacy Policy page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
